<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>{{title}}: {{language}}</title>
</head>
<body style="margin: 30px;">
    <h3>{{title}}</h3>
    <p>An experiment to see how Container Interop Service Provider could work.</p>
    <p>See <a href="https://github.com/container-interop/service-provider" target="_blank">here</a> for more info.</p>
    <hr>
    <h1><a title="&quot;Hello World&quot; in {{language}}">{{greeting}}</a></h1>
    <p><em>Language: "{{language}}"</em></p>
    <p>
        Append to the URL: <pre>?lang='xx'</pre> (replacing "xx" with a supported language)
        to see the greeting on this page shown in a different language.
    </p>
    <p>
        Supported languages are:<br>
        <ul>
            {{#languages}}
            <li><a href="{{base_url}}?lang={{.}}">{{.}}</a></li>
            {{/languages}}
        </ul>
    </p>
    <p>
        Requiring un unsupported language will trigger an exception. (<a href="{{base_url}}?lang=xxx">Try</a>).
    </p>
    <p>
        <small>
            Translations provided by
            <a href="https://translate.google.com" target="_blank">Google Translate</a>
        </small>
    </p>
    <hr>
    <p><a href="{{index_url}}">&laquo; Back to experiments index</a></p>
</body>
</html>